# Create and Update Category Form in Admin Dashboard

## Admin Page Depiction

The page should have this fields. The data would be sent as a FormData by the frontend project.

### Fields

- Title: required
- Slug: required
- Description: required
- There is no courses count field, because new category should have 0 courses assigned

## Actions

- Create, fix, and maintain the category creation, update, and deletion logic in `CourseCategoryController`. Don't forget to keep the controller lean. Utilize the `Services` and `Repositories`
- Validate the request body with the Laravel Request validation feature, before proceeding with any query and mutation
